These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, rat, goldfish
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, apricot, coral, brown
1. the owner of the rat is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes apricot##2
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
3. the person who likes coral is not to the left of the person who likes coral##8
4. the person who likes apricot is not the owner of the rat##6
5. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Pet   | goldfish  | guinea-pig | rat | lizard  |
| Color   | green | coral   | brown  | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, bus, boat
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, dog, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
2. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
3. the person driving the car is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the car and the person driving the quad-bike##2
5. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the owner of the chinchilla##7
6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
7. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Transport   | bus | quad-bike          | boat | car     |
| Pet    | dog      | rat | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, lily, azalea
4 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, mouse, bird
1. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
7. the person who growsazalea is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Flower           | zinnia | orchid | lily     | azalea |
| Pet   | goldfish    | bird   | horse | mouse    |

