.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, mauve, apricot, azure
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis, dahlia, begonia
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who growsorchid is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person who likes azure is not to the right of the person who growsdahlia##8
5. the person who likes coral is the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | apricot   | mauve         | azure   | coral    |
| Flower         | amaryllis | begonia | dahlia | orchid |

