.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, baccarat, dannemann, tiparillo
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, traveling, camping, baking
1. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the oliveros-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##7
2. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
3. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the dannemann-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##7
4. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
5. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the baccarat-smoker and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar   | baccarat   | dannemann | tiparillo | oliveros    |
| Hobby         | video-games | baking   | camping   | traveling |

