.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, chess, snooker
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, italian, chinese, argentine
1. the argentine is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the italian is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the chinese##3
5. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
6. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the italian##8
7. the person playing snooker is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Game          | snooker | scrabble | mah-jongg  | chess |
| Nationality   | italian   | argentine         | chinese | pakistani |

