.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, country, r&b, gospel
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, writing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the fan of country##8
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the fan of country##8
6. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
8. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country      | r&b | funk | gospel   |
| Hobby      | baking | writing | woodworking  | board-games |

