.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, december, october
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, aristoff, ritmeester, oliveros
1. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the oliveros-smoker##8
2. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the aristoff-smoker and the person who's birthday is in september##7
5. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the aristoff-smoker and the person who's birthday is in december##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Birthday     | september | december | october | march     |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | ritmeester        | oliveros          | aristoff |

