.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, collecting, magic-tricks, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, october, march
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's birthday is in november##2
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
8. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing   | skydiving | magic-tricks | collecting |
| Birthday     | march | february       | november  | october    |

