.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cherry, cucumber, pepper
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, salsa, funk, pop
1. the person eating pepper is between the fan of salsa and the fan of funk##2
2. the fan of punk is not the person eating cherry##6
3. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the person eating cauliflower##8
5. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
6. the fan of salsa is not to the right of the fan of punk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food         | cucumber | cauliflower      | pepper   | cherry  |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | salsa | punk | funk |

