3. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
4. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
5. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
