.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, may, october
4 different games are played: billiard, go, chess, poker
1. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
2. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
4. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person playing poker and the person playing chess##2
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday    | february        | october | may      | january    |
| Game   | billiard | chess   | go | poker |

