.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, engineer, lawyer, musician
House: futuristic, townhouse, tower, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the futuristic house##8
2. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the security-guard##8
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the engineer##1
4. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
5. the musician is on the far left or far right##3
6. the futuristic house is somewhere between the tower house and the engineer##7
7. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the engineer##3
8. the musician is on the left or right of the engineer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Job   | musician | engineer         | lawyer    | security-guard       |
| House      | townhouse | ranch-style | futuristic | tower |

