.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, apple, carrot, grapefruit
City: edinburgh, miami, colone, prague
1. the person traveling to prague is not to the left of the person traveling to miami##8
2. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
4. the person eating apple is between the person eating grapefruit and the person traveling to colone##2
5. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to miami and the person traveling to prague##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food   | lime     | apple | grapefruit        | carrot       |
| City      | colone | miami  | edinburgh | prague |

