.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, surfing, rugby, volleyball
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bolivar, tiparillo, old-henry
 1. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
 5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##8
 9. the bolivar-smoker is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
10. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Sport          | surfing    | rugby | parkour | volleyball |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | old-henry  | tiparillo     | bolivar    |

