4. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
6. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the palace house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | ice-hockey | weightlifting  | water-polo  |
| House   | gothic-revival | townhouse   | palace | cottage |

