.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, daffodil, amaryllis
4 different games are played: billiard, canasta, monopoly, scrabble
1. the person playing canasta is not the person who growsiris##6
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
4. the person who growsdaffodil is the person playing billiard##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person playing billiard##7
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing scrabble and the person who growsdaffodil##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Flower         | azalea    | amaryllis | iris | daffodil |
| Game   | canasta | scrabble      | monopoly     | billiard     |

 